data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sitting on almost a 1/2 an acre with no HOA outshines new construction with its remarkable upgrades. As you enter through the glass front door, you're greeted by two spacious bedrooms and a bathroom on your right, while the master bedroom and laundry are on your left. Down the hall, an inviting open floor plan awaits, seamlessly connecting the kitchen and living space, complete with a generous island for gatherings. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite counters, soft-close shaker cabinets, and 5 1/4 inch baseboards throughout. The master bedroom offers a large walk-in closet and an ensuite with a double vanity and tiled shower. Relax on the 27x28 screened back patio with ceramic tile flooring surrounded by lush landscaping in the fully fenced yard. Minutes away from the St. Johns River, downtown Deland, and a soon-to-open Sunrail station. Don't let this perfect sanctuary slip away!
